prompt.title: Embedding for Book: AI-Friendly Markup Language
prompt.content: The Book language is a human-understandable markup language for creating AI applications such as chatbots, knowledge bases, agents, and automations. It is based on markdown and designed to be easily readable by both humans and machines.
